CREATE TABLE `doc-ai-studio.qsight_test.Device`
(
  DeviceId STRING NOT NULL,
  DepartmentId STRING NOT NULL,
  InventoryLocationId STRING,
  DeviceName STRING(50) NOT NULL,
  DeviceTypeId STRING NOT NULL,
  DeviceProviderId STRING NOT NULL,
  DeviceDefinitionId STRING(50) NOT NULL,
  DeviceSerialNumber STRING(255) NOT NULL,
  Region STRING(50) NOT NULL,
  ResponseId STRING(50),
  Inactive BOOL NOT NULL,
  DeviceParams STRING(2000),
  DateCreated TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  DateLastModified TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)
PARTITION BY DATE(DateCreated);
